'''hazmat'''
# [[hazardous materials|'''Haz'''ardous '''mat'''erial(s)]].

===Usage notes===
Often used adjectivally, as in the term [[hazmat suit]].  The term ''hazmat'' (also capitalized as ''HAZMAT'' or hyphenated as ''Haz-Mat'') is chiefly used in the U.S.; the equivalent term in the rest of the English-speaking world is [[dangerous goods]].